50:48.604 --> 50:53.207
and I love him.

50:53.242 --> 50:55.943
No.

50:55.978 --> 50:59.112
That's not love.

50:59.148 --> 51:01.048
That's torture.

51:14.830 --> 51:16.763
And why were you taking pictures of us?

51:16.799 --> 51:18.665
I was practicing my long lens technique

51:18.701 --> 51:20.100
at various shutter speeds

51:20.135 --> 51:21.468
when you and Dr. Dreessen

51:21.504 --> 51:25.138
just happened to barge
into frame, lips locked.

51:25.174 --> 51:26.974
Is there some crime against kissing?

51:27.009 --> 51:29.943
No, but if Dr. Masters
and Mrs. Johnson find out

51:29.979 --> 51:34.114
I kept something
like this from them, well,

51:34.149 --> 51:36.517
I don't want to tell.

51:36.552 --> 51:39.086
But if you won't,

51:39.121 --> 51:42.689
I won't have any choice.

51:51.166 --> 51:52.533
I don't understand.

51:52.568 --> 51:55.536
They're married.

51:55.571 --> 51:57.204
To each other.

51:57.239 --> 52:00.874
I just spoke with Nancy
and she confessed to it all.

52:02.144 --> 52:04.444
I don't know what to say.

52:04.480 --> 52:06.213
And I don't know what we should do.

52:06.248 --> 52:07.681
There's only one thing to do.

52:07.716 --> 52:11.118
We can't allow our employees to lie.

52:11.153 --> 52:13.820
We'll have to let them both go.

52:13.856 --> 52:15.222
I'll bring them in here now.

52:15.257 --> 52:17.224
Bill, before you do...

52:17.259 --> 52:18.959
If they lied to us about this,

52:18.994 --> 52:21.061
who knows what they're capable of?

52:21.096 --> 52:23.130
But if we gave them a chance...

52:23.165 --> 52:24.631
Why would we do that?

52:24.667 --> 52:26.400
Because I'm sure they had their reasons.

52:26.435 --> 52:30.304
Everyone who lies has reasons.

52:30.339 --> 52:31.972
All I'm saying is I'm sure

52:32.007 --> 52:33.907
they would have told
the truth eventually.

52:33.943 --> 52:35.542
And why would you be so sure of that?

52:35.578 --> 52:38.278
Because people can't live
with a lie forever.

52:50.192 --> 52:54.261
So that's your decision?

52:54.296 --> 52:56.763
Well, I think...

52:56.799 --> 53:00.267
since you have spoken to
Nancy, I'll speak to Art.

53:00.302 --> 53:03.103
We'll let them both know
that they are on notice

53:03.138 --> 53:05.939
and then we move on.

53:15.217 --> 53:19.119
To say that we are disappointed

53:19.154 --> 53:21.388
would be an understatement.

53:21.423 --> 53:24.424
I don't recall ever seeing
Dr. Masters so upset.

53:24.460 --> 53:25.959
I can explain.

53:25.995 --> 53:28.962
I'm uninterested in your
reasons for lying.

53:28.998 --> 53:31.865
If it were up to Dr. Masters
you would be fired.

53:31.900 --> 53:35.135
And I agree with him.

53:35.170 --> 53:37.070
But given I have

53:37.106 --> 53:40.240
a more compassionate nature...

53:40.275 --> 53:41.170
I can see that you do.

53:41.171 --> 53:44.077
I might be willing to
fight for you and Nancy

53:44.113 --> 53:48.081
but it would require you
never lying to us again.

53:48.117 --> 53:49.716
Yes, that is understood.

53:49.752 --> 53:53.754
And I would also have
to know that you understand

53:53.789 --> 53:57.958
the importance in
this office of discretion,

53:57.993 --> 54:00.293
and for example, I would need to know

54:00.329 --> 54:03.130
that you would never mention to anyone

54:03.165 --> 54:06.299
seeing me last night.

54:07.536 --> 54:09.736
Last night?

54:09.772 --> 54:10.771
Of course not.

54:10.806 --> 54:12.239
I... I have no intention.

54:12.274 --> 54:14.675
What you saw...

54:14.710 --> 54:17.110
Well, my husband and I,

54:17.146 --> 54:19.613
we have an agreement,

54:19.648 --> 54:21.148
an arrangement,

54:21.183 --> 54:23.617
and that is nobody's
business but our own.

54:23.652 --> 54:26.353
Please, you don't have to explain.

54:26.388 --> 54:28.021
In the interest of never lying again,

54:28.057 --> 54:32.159
I'll tell you I'm
also in an open marriage.

54:32.194 --> 54:35.328
So I judge no one, ever,

54:35.364 --> 54:37.330
when it comes to these things.

54:41.136 --> 54:44.471
All right then.

54:44.506 --> 54:47.040
So we understand each other.

